name: BabyDoge CEO
description: BabyDoge CEO is cute but with a lot of BITE! $BCEO is a deflationary token designed to become more scarce over time. All holders of BabyDoge CEO will earn more $BCEO that is automatically sent to your wallet by simply holding BabyDoge CEO token in your wallet. Watch the amount of BabyDoge CEO grow in your wallet as BabyDoge CEO holders automatically receive a 3% fee from every on chain transaction that happens on the Baby Doge ecosystem. The community receives more BabyDoge CEO from the fees generated each transaction.
